    "Html": "<p>I've noticed quite a few people asking about credentials modifications.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nFor Forms&nbsp;Authentication out&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.dotnetjunkies.com/WebLog/joshuagough/archive/2006/01/20/134825.aspx\">http://www.dotnetjunkies.com/WebLog/joshuagough/archive/2006/01/20/134825.aspx</a><br>\r\n<br>\r\nHere is a modification I used&nbsp;to add&nbsp;credentials to the Web Request.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nIn HtmlWeb.cs:<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n1.) create&nbsp;the following private fields:&nbsp;<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">private</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">string</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> _userName;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">private</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">string</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> _password;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n2.) Create a new constructor:&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">public</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> HtmlWeb(</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">string</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> userName, </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">string</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> password)\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>{</p>\r\n<p>_userName = userName;</p>\r\n<p>_password = password;</p>\r\n<p>}<br>\r\n<br>\r\n3.)&nbsp;Add the following to the&nbsp;HttpStatusCode Get() method<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>private</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">HttpStatusCode</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> Get(</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">Uri</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> uri, </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">string</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> method, </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">string</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> path, </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">HtmlDocument</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> doc)\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>{</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px\">&nbsp;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">if</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">(!</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">string</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">.IsNullOrEmpty(_userName) &amp;&amp; !</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">string</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">.IsNullOrEmpty(_password))\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>{</p>\r\n<p>req.Credentials = </p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">new</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#2b91af\">NetworkCredential</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">(_userName, _password);\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>}</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n",
